; File: lotus.lg

; File Description: The fiel contains the procedure LOTUS :size that when invoked
; creates a 8 diamonds with sides of length :size.

; Imports the file diamond.lg
LOAD "diamond.lg

; The procedure below creates a lotus uses the procedure DIAMOND :size.
TO LOTUS :size

; Iterates 8 times and calls the procedure to draw a dimand with
; sides of size :size.
REPEAT 8 [DIAMOND :size]

end